divs: sighting details*on film* unkown objects in front of the sun during the transit of venus. i had recently filmed the transit of venus on 6\5\12 on the east coast of the u.s. that day happened to be very cloudy so i had to wait hours for a break in the clouds to capture the transit. well i had a break in the clouds for about a few minutes and grabbed the opportuniy. after the recording i let the tapes sit around for months until yesterday christmas eve. when i reviewed the footage i noticed two strange objects other than venus. the objects appeared to be equally placed within the suns round shape. i thought sun spots but these two objects seem mathematically placed. i also noticed two additional objects off on their own in front of the sun totaling 5 objects including venus. the footage is in beautiful 1080 hd quality. the suns placement at the time of filmming placed it rite near commercial jet lanes and you can see jets move close and far within the frames. the objects seem to not move like they are in front of the sun. who should i contact to take a look at the footage?
Summary: 5 objects on film in front of the sun- Venus and 4 smaller objects.
